CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 5, 1963, pg. 6, reads: "Stork Shower - Members of Iota Chapter, Alpha Kappa Alpha Sorority, the University of Pittsburgh, gave a 'Stork Shower,' recently honoring Mrs. Jacqueline James, at the honoree's home, Oakwood St.  Seated, left to right: Sorors Sandra Gibson, chapter president; Barbara Payne, Carolyn Brock, Zenobia Harper, Mrs. James, the honoree; Agnes Mason, Linda and Gwen Cartledge.  Standing: Cecilia [Cecelia] Champ, chairman of the affair; Judith Nelson and Claudia Harper. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Alpha Kappa Alpha, Iota Chapter members at baby shower for Jacqueline James, seated from left: Sandra Gibson, Barbara Payne, Carolyn Brock, Zenobia Harper, Jacqueline James, Agnes Mason, Linda Cartledge, Gwen Cartledge; standing: Cecelia Champ, Judith Nelson, and Claudia Harper, in James home, Oakwood Street
